OL,6,FA veteran received a surprise visit
OL,7,Ffrom family and friends to celebrate
OL,8,Fhis 100th birthday on Wednesday 7
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FWell wishers from the UK, Scotland,
OL,12,Fand Australia gathered to celebrate
OL,13,FTom Morris' centenary event.
OL,15,FTom was born on 7 February 1924 - the
OL,16,Feldest of four siblings, who all
OL,17,Fattended his party.
OL,19,FHe actively served during , before
OL,20,Freturning to Guernsey to work for
OL,21,FStates Work.
