OL,6,FIn reaching his 100th birthday, Tom
OL,7,Fhas received a message from the
OL,8,FGovernor of Guernsey as well as a
OL,9,Fpersonalised card from .
OL,11,FTom said: "I did try to phone (King
OL,12,FCharles), but he's busy."
OL,14,FAmong the party attendees was Tom's
OL,15,Fnephew, John Morris from Australia who
OL,16,Fsaid: "I've been planning it for the
OL,17,Fpast 12 months but I wanted it to be a
OL,18,Fsurprise for him."
